item.title: Report X-2024030589
item.description:
Report X-2024030589

Identified by scraper @ 2024-03-15T15:11:11+00:00

  • Incident Date: 2024-03-08
  • City: KENAI
  • State: AK
  • Report Type: Undeclared Shipment with no Release
  • Mode Of Transportation: Air
  • Carrier/Reporter: UNITED PARCEL SERVICE CO.
  • Hazmat Fatalities: 0
  • Hazmat Injuries: 0
  • Non-Hazmat Fatalities: 0
  • Description: AT THE UPS FACILITY IN KENAI, ALASKA, ONE PACKAGE WAS DROPPED SPILLING THE INNER CONTENTS. UPON INSPECTION OF THE CONTENTS DISCOVERED ONE MW37V22-N LITHIUM ION BATTERY. PACKING SLIP INSIDE THE PACKAGE DESCRIBES THE CONTENTS AS ONE LITHIUM ION BATTERY. THERE ARE NO DANGEROUS GOODS MARKS OR LABELS ON THE OUTER PACKAGE. PRIOR TO THE UNDECLARED DISCOVERY THE PACKAGE HAD FLOWN SDF TO ANC AND ANC TO ENA. THE PACKAGE WAS SHIPPED FROM ILLINOIS USING UPS ACCOUNT NUMBER 99F0V4, FIELD SHEER - SAN MARCOS, 2910 NORMAN STRASSE RD STE 1, SAN MARCOS CA 92069-5934.

  • Report Type: Undeclared Shipment with no Release
  • Mode Of Transportation: Air
  • Carrier/Reporter: UNITED PARCEL SERVICE CO.
  • Hazmat Fatalities: 0
  • Hazmat Injuries: 0
  • Non-Hazmat Fatalities: 0
  • Description: A PACKAGE FROM OREGON TO ALASKA MARKED AS CONTAINING CELLULAR ACCESSORIES WAS OUT FOR DELIVERY IN KENAI. THE DRIVER PICKED UP THE BOX AND CONTENTS OF THE PACKAGE SPILLED TO THE TRUCK FLOOR. PACKAGE WAS TRANSPORTED BACK TO THE UPS FACILITY AND INSPECTION REVEALED VARIOUS CELLULAR ACCESSORIES ALONG WITH EIGHT ACOUSTIX TRUE WIRELESS AUDIOBUDS + WITH CHARGING CASE INCLUDED. THERE ARE NO DANGEROUS GOODS MARKS OR LABELS ON THE OUTER BOX. THE PACKAGE WAS FLOWN ON UPS AIRCRAFT FROM ONT TO ANC AND ANC TO ENA.
